; general operations with explicit dispatch
; add new type -> changing all methods to handle them
; add new operation -> add new operation to handle this for all types
;
; data oriented programming
; add new type -> install new (separate) type that has all operations
; add new operation -> add new operation for each type
;
;
; message passing programming
; add new type -> create new type with operations
; add new operation -> add new operation for all types

; Easiest adding new type -> message passing programming
; Easiest adding new operation -> data oriented programming
